---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="美甲教學課程 | ITUNG NAILS 伊特美甲" description="ITUNG NAILS 伊特美甲提供美甲全科班、彩繪教學課程與穿戴甲教學。由經驗豐富的美甲師帶領，從基礎到進階。景美・新店兩店。">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-8 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <nav class="text-sm text-it-text mb-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-it-cta">首頁</a> <span class="mx-2">/</span> <span>美甲教學</span>
      </nav>
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-it-dark mb-4">美甲教學課程</h1>
        <p class="text-it-text max-w-2xl mx-auto">由經驗豐富的美甲師帶領，從基礎到進階，適合想學習美甲技術或轉職的朋友。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-it-secondary/20 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-it-secondary/30 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">🎓</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-it-dark mb-2">美甲全科班</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-it-text mb-4">從基礎保養、凝膠上色到進階彩繪，系統化學習專業美甲技術。</p>
          <a href="https://lin.ee/OCPxzKS" target="_blank" class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-it-cta text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-it-cta/90 transition-colors">洽詢課程</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-it-secondary/20 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-it-secondary/30 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">🖌️</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-it-dark mb-2">彩繪教學課程</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-it-text mb-4">學習手繪技巧，從簡單線條到複雜的藝術設計，如油畫玫瑰、花磚、動漫角色等。</p>
          <a href="https://lin.ee/OCPxzKS" target="_blank" class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-it-cta text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-it-cta/90 transition-colors">洽詢課程</a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-it-secondary/20 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-it-secondary/30 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">💅</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-it-dark mb-2">穿戴甲教學</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-it-text mb-4">學習穿戴甲的製作、配戴與卸除技巧，適合想創業或自用的朋友。</p>
          <a href="https://lin.ee/OCPxzKS" target="_blank" class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-it-cta text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-it-cta/90 transition-colors">洽詢課程</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 bg-it-light rounded-2xl p-8 border border-it-secondary/20">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-it-dark mb-4 text-center">學員常見問題</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm text-it-text">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-it-dark mb-1">沒有基礎可以學嗎？</p>
            <p>當然可以！課程從基礎開始教學，無經驗也能上手。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-it-dark mb-1">需要自備工具嗎？</p>
            <p>基礎課程提供練習工具，進階課程會建議購買個人工具組。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-it-dark mb-1">上課地點在哪？</p>
            <p>課程於景美店或新店店進行，報名時確認上課地點。</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-it-dark mb-1">如何報名？</p>
            <p>請透過 LINE 私訊預約諮詢，我們會依您的需求規劃課程。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
